      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THINK LU BELLA (8) ran a very good race first up at Murray Bridge over 1400m, getting home nicely for second to be beaten just a nose giving every indication she'd relish the step up to a mile here. She should land in a handy spot here and take catching. SHAMASTAR (4) comes here off a good debut at Naracoorte, getting home well to grab third over 1430m. Bit tougher here but he should improve nicely here and the Pannell/Hickmott combination are a strong one. ROYAL MUSE (6) presents third up having bumped into a good winner over this route last time out. Peaks now and draws to effect. STARSCREAM (2) was just fair fresh at Murray Bridge over 1200m, sharply up in trip here with added fitness. He can improve. VANINETTI (3) should appreciate the rise to a mile third up.",
